data.description: This spacious home features a popular floor plan that includes a generous great room and a downstairs guest bedroom with a full bath. The modern kitchen offers sleek stainless steel appliances (including a gas range), recessed can lighting, and 30-in. maple cabinets in Espresso. The luxurious master bath boasts a walk-in shower. You will also discover exquisite natural-tone tile flooring throughout the entire downstairs area and upstairs in the master bath, secondary bath and laundry room. Upgraded Shaw® carpeting and padding in the master bedroom and secondary bedrooms fills out the impressive details on the second floor. Additional features include two tone interior paint, ceiling fan pre-wiring, and Cat-5 pre-wiring throughout. This home will be available for move-in July/August.
